text: Hempstead is a village and civil parish in Uttlesford, Essex, England. In 2001 there were 422 people living in Hempstead. It is 7 miles east of Saffron Walden.http://www.hempstead-essex.org.uk/ == References == Category:Uttlesford Category:Villages in Essex Category:Civil parishes in Essex
